title: Bidinthani gelenayao . . .
lyrics:
Bidinthani gelenayao . . . 2
Buhumao subunga gwmalangjwbbai -2
(A)
Swr naigirw nwngkhou
Swr kulumw nwngkhou
Oh . . . . .  swr dongw,
swithw arw dhwrwmkhou sibigwra
Isorni huda khou manigwra
Raobw gwiya . . . be buhumao
(B)
Swr naigirw nwngkhou
Swr sibiyw nwngkhou
Oh . . . . .  Bifa Isor
Adri dakhalam jwngkhou kholaiyw nwng
Dagalang be khwmsi buhumao nwng
Githaobathao be buhumao
